 name it.</li>\n<li>Called out the grifting EU and their installed leaders so now they will be forced to pay for their own defense AND come to grips with their huge socialist spending budgets.</li>\n<li>Ultimate goal with Iran. Reacquire ALL their uranium. Prove that its original source was the USA (by using isotope identification) facilitated by CLINTONS AND OBAMA. Treason. Death penalty.</li>\n<li>With all the foreigners under economic stress, US Dollar will get stronger and stronger while we repatriate 100,000+ manufacturing jobs. USA economy grows and flourishes while deportations accelerate at historical rates boosting pay for all US workers who wont pay Federal taxes on tips or Overtime pay.</li>\n<li>The housing availability with explode while costs and rent drop as Federal subsidies to illegal immigrants dry up.</li>\n<li>Food prices will drop due to illegal immigrants SNAP $ going away.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>MAGA! Its all part of the plan and IT IS WORKING!</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 8, "score_up": 59, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2058595725118734563", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASsZF0Heq", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 97, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8638718, "raw_content": "", "author": "PiratePatriotParrot", "created": 1779699819546, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "cashisking", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASsZF0Heq.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/PapiTrumpo/status/2058595725118734563?s=20", "author_